lead_paragraph: Elin Gustavsson had 21 points and seven rebounds and No. 22 Colorado State won its 26th straight in a 53-41 victory over eighth-seeded San Diego State on Tuesday in the quarterfinals of the Mountain West Conference tournament.

headline.print_headline: No. 22 Colorado State Women Beat Aztecs 53-41 in MWC Semis
